g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca03507f92c58630f16ae3895a60651b44fa390","tid":368053,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌<br />\n睇個傷hi親下咋wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再遲少少成隻手俾隻熊扯走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一拳打落佢個鼻就得</blockquote><br />\n五毛狗狗吠就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}